      "notes": "Hsunchen (Beast People) — Neolithic hunter-gatherers. Totemic wolf identity. Cursed Strain in Dragon Pass: every Wildday (full Lunar Moon) they metamorphose into full lupine form (Lycanthropy rules from RUNEQUEST p.396). Nysalor blessed their wolf-form hides to be impervious to bronze, bone, stone, wood, flesh or claw. Later cursed by Talor the Laughing Warrior. Practice Animism through Korgatsu Spirit Tradition.",
